<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Bupa Care Home Application</title>
</head>
<body>

<h2>Bupa Care Home Application</h2>

<form>
<label>Full Name</label><br>
<input type="text" placeholder="Enter your full name"><br><br>

<label>Phone Number</label><br>
<input type="tel" placeholder="Enter your phone number"><br><br>

<label>Home Address</label><br>
<input type="text" placeholder="Enter your address"><br><br>

<label>Proof of Address</label><br>
<input type="file"><br><br>

<button type="submit">Submit Application</button>
</form>

<h3>After submitting:</h3>
<p>Thank you. Your application has been received successfully.</p>
<p>Please wait while our team reviews your documents. We will contact you if your application is successful.</p>

</body>
</html>
